QUANTITATIVE TRADING PLATFORM
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td height="32"></td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td style="font-size:16px;color:#e5e7eb;">
Dear {{name}},
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td height="16"></td>
</tr>

