Welcome to <strong style="color:#38bdf8;">UPIS Delta</strong>.  
Your account has been successfully created.
<br><br>
Before accessing the platform, please verify your email address.
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td height="30"></td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td align="center">

<a href="{{domain}}/api/auth/verify/{{verifyToken}}"
style="
background:#38bdf8;
color:#020617;
text-decoration:none;
padding:14px 32px;
border-radius:8px;
font-size:15px;
font-weight:700;
display:inline-block;
letter-spacing:0.4px;
">
Verify Account </a>

</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td height="30"></td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td style="font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8;line-height:1.6;">
If the button above does not work, copy the link below and open it in your browser:
<br><br>

<span style="color:#38bdf8;">
{{domain}}/api/auth/verify/{{verifyToken}}
</span>

</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td height="40"></td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td style="border-top:1px solid #1f2937;padding-top:22px;">

<table width="100%">

<tr>

<td style="font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8;">
UPIS Delta
<br>
Quantitative research & algorithmic trading infrastructure
</td>

<td align="right" style="font-size:12px;color:#64748b;">
© 2026 UPIS Delta
<br>
All rights reserved
</td>

</tr>

<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="padding-top:16px;font-size:12px;color:#64748b;line-height:1.6;">
This email was sent because an account was created using this address.  
If you did not initiate this request, you may safely ignore this message.
</td>
</tr>

</table>

</td>
</tr>

</table>

</td>
</tr>
